title: Kakutou Bijin Wulong: Rebirth (Fighting Beauty Wulong Rebirth)
synopsis: Mao Lan continues growing into her path in life through what she learns while fighting. Her grandfather thinks that she has grown complacent and decides to train an adversary for her next Prime Mat appearance. Training with her friends and companions Mao Lan slowly advances through life.
